{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1740208672.811347","card_id":"Q_12921707799","target":{"id":12921707799,"title":"如何看待俞敏洪质疑「被看重的年轻人并未全身心投入工作」，董明珠称「是社会物质丰富了」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/12921707799","type":"question","created":1740121317,"answer_count":271,"follower_count":439,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2566,27919,95092,212180,1328924],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2月20日，《酌见》栏目发布了董明珠与俞敏洪对话片段。 在对话中，董明珠与俞敏洪探讨了职场年轻人的工作态度问题。 俞敏洪问：“不明白为什么现在的小年轻被人看上了，却没有全身心地投入去做？并且给自己足够时间去证明自己？” 董明珠认为是环境问题，“是社会物质丰富了，他们会觉得我这么努力，那些不努力的人为什么比我要好？”董明珠与俞敏洪对话片段曝光！董明珠：已经找到格力接班人，有三四个预备人选！谈到遗憾，两人这样说…"},"attached_info":"CkIIirKajNGrv8c9EAMaCTExMzU1OTkxNyDlyeC9BjAAOLcDQAByCzEyOTIxNzA3Nzk5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"415 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-633fe13a85079a80c9db868a91ad013f_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1740208672.812215","card_id":"Q_351874821","target":{"id":351874821,"title":"哪吒的母亲是李靖原配，为什么大家称她为殷夫人而不是李夫人？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/351874821","type":"question","created":1571708444,"answer_count":259,"follower_count":365,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5753,5823,16927,154582,156312],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IirKajNGrv8c9EAMaCDQwNDcyNTc5IJy8ue0FMAA47QJAAXIJMzUxODc0ODIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"323 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b4a4f5046ab68bdac79297141269b91f_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1740208672.812432","card_id":"Q_12966983763","card_label":{"type":"